{
  "stem": "26765.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What stands out about Bergen-Belsen is the, the hunger.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were only talking about food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, people ask me, well, what did you think about?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Potatoes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Only potatoes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we thought about getting out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We always had hope that we would get out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I think that that helped us survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "As. as for me, like I say, I can't speak for my brother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But as for me, I never doubted that we would not survive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- but we only thought, my only thought, was about potatoes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] George did say to me that, you know, if I hadn't been there, he would be able, he would have been able to escape.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He, he thought, you know, that without me there, he would have been able to escape.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I doubt that very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But, you know, he was, at that time, 14 years old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you know, perhaps he thought he could have escaped.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But there were armed guards within-- everywhere, surrounding the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was electrified barbed wire all around us, two feet deep.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was no way that we could have escaped.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then, in the spring of 1945, I remember that we had to line up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we were going to get an injection in our arm, like an immunization.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I overheard people say that this is an immunization against typhoid.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now, you know typhoid and typhus was just raging throughout the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Diarrhea, and people were dying left and right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And so, we lined up, and they injected us with that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Of course, there was-- there still is no inoculation against typhoid or typhus.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And pretty soon thereafter, we were put on a train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And this was April 10th now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We were put on a train.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
